&gt;1.5</entry><entry>Either install <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1427_4.6.0.xml#_710062da-7211-491f-ad4c-b3f12b9b96bb" id="_cf5ae953-72ae-4273-91ee-b24c7845a42e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">reflective insulation</xref> outside the frame to create a minimum 20 mm reflective airspace between frame and cladding, or add a layer of continuous insulation with an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_42f326a2-a58d-4199-bb6e-2394bd46bf84" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref> of at least R0.30 on the inside or the outside of the frame.</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table><desc-note id="_7979fbb0-cfe8-4983-b6e4-21d2ac7ab5db"><ol outputclass="numbered"><li id="_22b07e5b-e806-4dfd-8807-a20531e949ef">Minimum <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_f8e4db38-a229-4d69-95f9-f15800f74435" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref>s are in-situ values. They account for compression of insulation.</li><li id="_fb61a32f-bdbf-4a36-8146-4d4da3925b17">The surface emittance of a reflective surface facing an airspace must be a maximum of 0.1.</li></ol></desc-note></table-reference>